uk.ac.ebi.pride.jmztab.utils.parser

Class MZTabLineParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.ebi.pride.jmztab.utils.parser.MZTabLineParser
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    COMLineParser, MTDLineParser, MZTabDataLineParser, MZTabHeaderLineParser

    public class MZTabLineParser
extends java.lang.Object
    Common tab split line parser. If there exists format or logical errors during the parse process, system will add them into MZTabErrorList, or break validate and throw MZTabException directly.
    See Also:
    MZTabHeaderLineParser, MZTabDataLineParser, User: Qingwei Date: 10/02/13
